To EUHFORIA output (dsv files) into OpenGGCM readable format:
Step 1: Convert EUHFORIA HEEQ data (hsphere.dsv file) to GSE coordinates (euh_10min_gse.txt) using euhforia_heeq2gse.py
Step 2: Convert the GSE data (euh_10min_gse.py) to OpenGGCM input formating satfilter_euh.py

The folders Event1 and Event2 contain the input files and the setup file used for OpenGGCM simulations in the paper.
>> runme file
>> For EUHFORIA data: euh.bxgse, euh.bygse, euh.bzgse, etc
>> For WIND or OMNI data: wi.bxgse or omni.bxgse etc
